the best mark in the county this year -- and also won the discus in 156-2 1/2. 
Teammate Damon Richardson won the 300 intermediate hurdles (41.5), Roshawn Sims 
won the 200 (22.2) and Trevor Lycett leaped 14-6 to win the pole vault for the 
Orange County-champion Aztecs (4-0). 
</P>
<P>
