jump and long jump to lead Orange at home. 
</P>
<P>
Kim Khaub won the 100 and 200, and Anthony Delacruz won the 110-meter high 
hurdles and the pole vault to help Orange. 
</P>
<P>
Pacific Coast League girls: 
</P>
<P>
