ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Edward C. Rizzotti has been appointed senior vice president for MagneTek 
Defense Systems and general manger of MagneTek Anaheim. 
</P>
<P>
He was previously vice president, government systems. Before joining MagneTek 
in 1988, he was with the electronics systems division of the consulting firm of 
Booz, Allen and Hamilton. In addition, Joseph A. Westrich was named vice 
president and assistant general manager. He has been with MagneTek for 25 years 
in various positions. 
</P>
